{"tid":42971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"花大錢搞婚禮不如幫窮人　印度外父起屋送暖","createTime":"2016-12-17T06:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T08:35:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59abe1643768ec1bac5596555bcae5e525eb77ec","tid":42971,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:42:04.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=ef5d3565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 結婚是人生大事，在印度，富裕家庭更會把婚禮辦得非常奢華。不過，當地有一名新外父，將原本可以用來為女兒「豪辦」婚禮的錢，捐作慈善用途，建屋送給無家可歸的人，將喜悅心情分享開去。 <br />\n<br />\n阿賈伊（Ajay Munot）是專門做布料與小麥交易的生意人，而最近他的女兒舒蕾亞（Shreya）要結婚了。在這場值得慶賀的大事中，阿賈伊就決定，與其將大筆金錢花在婚禮上，不如將那筆近90萬港元的金錢，用作興建一個住宅區，供無家可歸的人居住。住宅區包含90棟房屋，每間面積約240平方呎，亦有潔淨的清水與充足電力提供。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，阿賈伊指這些房屋也有入住條件，他們都必須是貧窮、正住在貧民窟的人，而且亦不能是癮君子，好讓那些房屋可以幫助到真正有需要的人。 <br />\n<br />\n舒蕾亞對父親這個決定感到非常滿意，她指這是一份很棒的新婚禮物。在婚禮後，舒蕾亞就聯同新婚丈夫一同將房屋鎖匙送到人們手中。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161216/bknint-20161216153428107-1216_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161216%2Fbknint-20161216153428107-1216_17011_001.html&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=f5ec2e7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161216/bknint-20161216153428107-1216_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"be5818999046b1c1c7b8f782fa38c18264c10a3f","tid":42971,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"強姦佢個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa79b3ece307486a1d103182409635847669781d","tid":42971,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"發財立品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846fcfa12b9ba88c914ff13c2b5cced90f600c1e","tid":42971,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181c07f0a5f6565684be3336648d820e151ba2df","tid":42971,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強姦佢個女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a70c9a4851c76dacadf1a4b2995b8c6289f5c9","tid":42971,"uid":8294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"九十萬一個住宅區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港廁所都買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}